snippet.title: Behind the Stumbles Part 1: What is Fall Guys?
snippet.description:
What is Fall Guys? Join Jeff (Creative Director) and Joe (Lead Designer) as they chat through the original Fall Guys pitch and share some excellent British buffoonery via old clips of the TV game show It’s A Knockout.

Coming to PlayStation 4 and Steam this summer! 
Wishlist: http://fallguys.com
Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/fallguys
